We format the data into panel data:

# Format the data into panel data
d <- CleanData(d,
    syndrome = "influensa",
    testIfHelligdagIndikatorFileIsOutdated = FALSE,
    removeMunicipsWithoutConsults = TRUE
  )

We run our analysis:

res <- sykdomspuls::QuasipoissonTrainPredictData(
  datasetTrain = d,
  datasetPredict = d,
  isDaily = F
)

print(res)
